                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/9201" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">MKT-1392</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">877 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">入湘随俗——泰康高端养老社区的营销发展之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">When in Hunan, do as the Hunanese do -- The marketing development of TAIKANG&#39;s High-end Retirement Communities</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">易丹，胡韩莉，胡俊，蔡亚男，曹泽纯</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">长沙理工大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">泰康之家湘园（长沙）养老服务有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">服务业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中小型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">19 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">养老服务；泰康；高端养老社区；营销战略；体验营销</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Elderly Care Services; TAIKANG; High-end retirement community; Marketing strategy; experience marketing</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">随着老龄化程度的逐步加深，人们对养老服务的需求也在不断增加，尽管普惠型养老服务的供给不断扩大，但个性化、多元化的高品质养老服务供给还存在较大缺口。在此背景下，泰康创新了“虚拟保险支付+实体医养康宁服务”的商业模式，并在多个城市打造高端养老社区，积累了丰富的经验。本文从泰康之家&#183;湘园的初创及发展过程入手，对泰康之家&#183;湘园的成立背景及原因，湘园采取哪些措施立足长沙市养老服务市场以及在遭遇营销瓶颈和盈利困境之后，如何通过新的营销方式挖掘潜在需求，怎样借助网红城市的流量打造IP主题等关键问题进行描述，引导学生依据PEST模型、STP理论、相关营销战略和马斯洛需求层次理论等分析问题与解决问题，提升学生理论与具体实际相结合的能力。同时，理解泰康高端养老社区在新一线城市的营销发展路径与战略，有助于引发关于白发经济浪潮下，养老服务企业如何找准自身定位、以老年群体现实需求为导向实现差异化经营的思考，为其营销策略的制定提供参考借鉴及新的思路。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">With the gradual deepening of aging, people&#39;s demand for senior care services has increased, and the supply of universal senior care services has been expanding, while the demand for personalised and diversified high-quality senior care services needs to be met. Against this backdrop, TAIKANG has innovated the business model of &quot;virtual insurance payment + physical healthcare and hospice services&quot;, and has built high-end senior living communities in many cities, accumulating a wealth of experience. This paper starts from the start-up and development process of Taikang Community Xiang Garden, describes the background and reasons for the establishment of Taikang Community Xiang Garden, the measures taken by Xiang Garden to gain a foothold in Changsha&#39;s senior care market, and how to explore the potential demand through new marketing methods after encountering marketing bottlenecks and profitability difficulties, how to create IP themes by using the traffic flow of the Netroots City, and guides the students to describe the business model based on PEST model, STP theory, relevant marketing strategies, and the development of the business model. Students are guided to analyse and solve problems based on the PEST model, STP theory, relevant marketing strategies and Maslow&#39;s hierarchy of needs theory, so as to enhance their ability to combine theory with concrete practice. Understanding the marketing development path and strategy of TAIKANG&#39;s High-end Retirement Communities in the new first-tier cities can help to trigger the thinking on how senior living service enterprises can find their own positioning and differentiate themselves with the real needs of the elderly groups under the economic wave, and provide references and new ideas for the development of their marketing strategies.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,博士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《管理学》、《市场营销》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">PEST模型；STP战略；蓝海战略；马斯洛需求层次理论；营销战略</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-01</td>
                            </tr>
